          "D_*^q X = f(X)",
          "D_*^q Phi = D_x f(X)*Phi, Phi(0)=I"
        ],
        "algorithm": "Benettin-Wolf with extended original+variational FO system, FDE12 ABM integration, Gram-Schmidt reorthonormalization",
        "finite_time_local": true,
